data.description: Wow!  Great price on this beautiful, well maintained 4bedroom/2 bath home with salt water inground pool!  High ceilings in living area with open concept.  Sellers have added many upgrades; Exterior house painted 2021, full outside kitchen, new roof 2018, pool cabana, pool pavers, variable speed pool pump. Plus more!  Extra Large lot to park your RV and or boat!  Plenty of parking, plus 2 car garage..  Private fenced backyard with outside kitchen/grill in pool area makes for  great for entertaining!  Easy to show!  Call today!  Note: All information & dimensions are deemed reliable but should be verified by Buyer.
